Our self-titled album will be coming on September 15. We’ve always intentionally had an air of mystery around us, but now we are more ourselves creatively and publicly than we’ve ever been. With this new album and the help of producer @mikeelizondojr, we’re all in. It’s time to lean in to who we are. Pre-order / pre-save / pre-add #BrothersOsborne now at the link in bio/stories.

But through it all, we are still us. For better and for worse at times. We self titled this album as it is the meeting point between who we’ve become, and who we’ve always been. Our music is Big Tent Country. A little something for everyone and everyone’s invited. We thank y’all for your patience, love, and unwavering support.
